          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "A 2018 Mercedes-AMG GT4 race car was inside a car trailer that was stolen with the truck from a parking lot recently. There are fewer than 200 examples like this in the world, and the owner is hoping someone will spot the ultra-race AMG.",
            "type": "text",
